* Dragan Crnogorac (police officer) – found guilty, sentenced to 13 years.<ref>{{cite news|title=Former Bosnian Serb police officer sentenced for Srebrenica war crimes|url=http://www.setimes.com/cocoon/setimes/xhtml/en_GB/newsbriefs/setimes/newsbriefs/2011/05/15/nb-06|newspaper=Southeast European Times|date=15 May 2011}}</ref>

